				<p rend="indent(1)">D<hi rend="sup">r</hi> Friend<add>&#63;</add><lb/> I hand you above my<lb/> check on Mechanic Bank <placeName>New York</placeName><lb/> for Ninety Seven 7<hi rend="underline">4</hi> Dollars for collecting<lb/> to date of Occident &#38; Jewish <sic>publication</sic><lb/> Society&#44; please send by return mail<lb/> Bill of <persName>David Lopez</persName> to date&#44; as he says<lb/> he has paid you some money for the<lb/> O&#44; &#38; the bill I printed he says is not right</p>
				<p rend="indent(1)"><persName>Mr Warners</persName> <date>July</date> no of the <sic>occident</sic> did<lb/> not come here did you send it <add>&#63;</add>&#44;<lb/> send me also bill of <persName>M Lazarus</persName> for Voice of<lb/> Jacob &#38; the <sic>sucessor</sic> to it&#44; or has the Journal<lb/> ceased&#44;&#63; as I have not received a number for<lb/> a long while&#44; Hoping you are well</p>
